contentrichtext.text: '''Oland''' may refer to: * [[Öland]], a Swedish island in the Baltic Sea ** [[County of Öland]], a former county of Sweden containing the island of Öland * [[Oland (Frisian island)]], a German island belonging to the North Frisian group * [[Oland Brewery]], a brewery in Halifax, Nova Scotia, Canada * [[Oland Hundred]], a district of Uppland, Sweden ==As a surname== * [[Philip Oland]] (1910–1996), a Canadian businessman * [[Victor de Bedia Oland]] (1913–1983), a Canadian politician * [[Warner Oland]] (1879–1938), a Swedish actor {{disambig}}
